OL,3,CPM wants to 'look again' at ECHR
OL,4,Cfollowing ITV News investigation
OL,6,FThe prime minister has said that he
OL,7,Fwants to "look again" at the European
OL,8,FConvention on Human Rights (ECHR),
OL,9,Fafter ITV News revealed cases of
OL,10,FBrazilian paedophiles and alleged
OL,11,Fmurderers using the convention to
OL,12,Favoid deportation from the UK.
OL,14,FKeir Starmer told the BBC that "we
OL,15,Fneed to look again at the
OL,16,Finterpretation of some of these
OL,17,Fprovisions, not tear them down".
