OL,6,FThe government had previously told ITV
OL,7,FNews that it was going to review the
OL,8,Fapplication of Article 3 of the
OL,9,Fconvention, protecting individuals
OL,10,Ffrom torture or inhumane treatment, as
OL,11,Fwell as Article 8, protecting the
OL,12,Fright to a family life.
OL,14,FNow, as a former human rights lawyer,
OL,15,FStarmer has added his voice to calls
OL,16,Fto re-examine the application of the
OL,17,FECHR.
