OL,6,FThe pair had argued they would face
OL,7,Fpoor treatment in Brazilian prisons,
OL,8,Fwhere overcrowding and violence are
OL,9,Fwell documented.
OL,11,FIn separate cases, both men were
OL,12,Fgranted the right to stay in Britain
OL,13,Funder Article 3, with Dos Santos going
OL,14,Fon to commit further crimes against
OL,15,Fchildren while working as a delivery
OL,16,Fdriver in London.
