OL,3,CPM wants to 'look again' at ECHR
OL,4,Cfollowing ITV News investigation
OL,6,FLast week, the new Home Secretary
OL,7,FShabana Mahmood told ITV News in her
OL,8,Ffirst interview in the role that she
OL,9,Fintended to set out further ideas
OL,10,Fabout reforming the ECHR later this
OL,11,Fautumn.
OL,13,FDesigned in the wake of World War II
OL,14,Fto prevent a repeat of horrific
OL,15,Fatrocities, the ECHR has more recently
OL,16,Fbeen criticised by some for allegedly
OL,17,Fpreventing states from controlling
OL,18,Ftheir borders.
