OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats and others -
OL,7,Fincluding many in the Labour Party -
OL,8,Fsay withdrawing would jeopardise human
OL,9,Frights and undermine the Good Friday
OL,10,FAgreement in Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FBut today's statements from Starmer
OL,13,Fsuggest he agrees with those on the
OL,14,Fcentre-right of the Labour Party that
OL,15,FECHR reform is necessary.
